<td colspan=3 class=black><br><p><font class=b>Objective</font><br><font class=black>
To play, build in sequence either up or down regardless of suit on the waste pile. For example, if the top of the waste pile is a 5, you can play either a 6 or a 4 on it.
The sequences do not "wrap around." Only a 2 can be played on an ace, and nothing can be played on a king.<br>
Whenever there are no possible plays, turn over a card in the Stock to the Waste pile. 
The game is won when all cards are sent to the single pile.








































































































































































































































































































